			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "They are 2 ways to trigger this dAD.\r\n1) Attack Orin before she spots you.\r\n2) Click the Dialog Attack button while in dialog with her.\r\n\r\nDifferent nodes is for when the players have a DU present during the initialition of this combat, or if the DU is somehow out of the temple."
				},
